INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (81751, 'I often wonder why the whole world is so prone to generalise. Generalisations are seldom if ever true and are usually utterly inaccurate.', 94, 0), (81752, 'All worthy work is open to interpretations the author did not intend. Art isn''t your pet -- it''s your kid. It grows up and talks back to you.', 1099, 0), (81753, 'You ride as a man, fight as a man, and you think as a man-""I think as a human being," she retorted hotly. "Men don''t think any differently from women- they just make more noise about being able to.', 2177, 0), (81754, 'Mother, who has an absolute belief that it is not the cards that one is dealt in life, it is how one plays them, is, by far, the highest card I was dealt.', 1631, 0), (81755, 'My aunt and overprivileged cousin only recognize two states of being: glitter and grunge. And if you weren’t glitter, well, that only left one other option.', 446, 0), (81756, 'He''s like Super Librarian, y''know? Everyone forgets, Willow, that knowledge is the ultimate weapon.', 1099, 0), (81757, 'The word “future” and females is a dangerous combination.', 936, 0), (81758, 'So here were the facts: I felt possessive of her. Not in a romantic sort of way, but in a "hit her over the head, drag her off by the hair, and fuck her" way. Like she was my toy and I was keeping the other boys in the sandbox from playing with her. How sick was that? If she ever heard me admit to that, she would cut off my balls and feed them to me.', 17039, 0), (81759, 'I didn''t set fire to the building.""No, but you did pull it into the river.""That put the fire out!', 1884, 0), (81760, 'You sure you don''t want me to bring you back something?" Her eyes moved in the direction of his office. "A hit man? Some holy water?', 17039, 0), (81761, 'This was the tricky bit. The really tricky bit, trickiness cubed.', 5933, 0), (81762, 'Edward lives as if there is no tomorrow, Richard as if he wants no tomorrow, and George as though someone should give it to him for free.', 605, 0), (81763, 'I''m Cinderella. No, I''m better than Cinderella, because she only got the prince, didn''t she? I''m Cinderella with fab teeth and a shit-hot job.', 173, 0), (81764, 'Go Ahead, call me all the names you want," Sansa said airily. "You won''t dare when I''m married to Joffrey. You''ll have to bow and call me Your Grace." She shrieked as Arya flung the orange across the table. It caught her in the middle of the forehead with a wet squish and plopped down into her lap."You have juice on your face, Your Grace ," Arya said.', 169, 0), (81765, 'If you tell me I''m sensible in addition to normal and wise, I''m going to punch you in the stomach.', 916, 0), (81766, 'If I''m out of my mind, it''s all right with me, thought Moses Herzog.', 653, 0), (81767, 'And what lesson can we draw from Volantene history?”“If you want to conquer the world, you best have dragons.', 169, 0), (81768, 'More of your conversation would infect my brain.', 13, 0), (81769, 'Now-what’s our game plan?”	Coach Hedge belched. He’d already had three espressos and a plate of doughnuts, along with two napkins and another flower from the vase on the table. He would’ve eaten the silverware, except Piper had slapped his hand.	“Climb the mountain,” Hedge said. “Kill everything except Piper’s dad. Leave.”	“Thank you General Eisenhower,” Jason grumbles.', 80, 0), (81770, 'Oh, I love hugging. I wish I was an octopus, so I could hug 10 people at a time!', 292, 0), (81771, 'Kaede: I know this, ungrateful dog. In order to find the sacred jewel shards, Kagome''s spirtual power is essential. Yet ye made her upset with your words an sent her running homeInuYasha: That was her idea! she chose to go home! She said: "I''m going home! You jerk!"Kaede: InuYasha, that imitation was pathetic.InuYasha: I''m a demon, not a comedian! ', 2235, 0), (81772, 'I also felt that Ron and Hermione would have gotten divorced. I''m sorry, I just do. The end of Harry Potter did fee